### Backend: Add `GET /api/users/search` mention support for comments

No new endpoint needed. The existing `GET /users/search?query=&limit=` (line 73 in routes.js, `searchUsersService` in getService.js) is public and returns `{ data: [{ id, name, username, image_url, badge }], hasMore }`. This is exactly what `useMentionAutocomplete` calls via `searchUsers()`.

