### Data Flow

```
User types "@jo" in comment textarea
  → onChange fires → setComments updated → mentionTextareaProps.onChange fires
  → setCursorPosition(selectionStart)
  → useMentionAutocomplete detects "@jo" via MENTION_TRIGGER_REGEX
  → 300ms debounce → searchUsers("jo", 6)
  → GET /api/users/search?query=jo&limit=6
  → results returned → MentionDropdown renders via portal
  → User presses ArrowDown / clicks result
  → handleSelect(user) called
  → value.substring(0, mentionStart) + "@johndoe " + rest
  → setComments(newValue) → React re-renders textarea
  → closeMenu() → dropdown unmounts
  → On submit → comment text contains "@johndoe" literally
  → Server addCommentService regex extracts username
  → Lookup user by username in users table
  → Insert mention notification
```

